WEBVTT

1
02:08:37.270 --> 02:08:39.100 
你知道奠边府战役吗?
You know anything about Dien Bien Phu?

2
02:08:42.300 --> 02:08:44.000 
-我知道  -不  你不知道
-Yeah, I know.  -No, you don't.

3
02:08:45.240 --> 02:08:46.210 
不真的知道
Not really.

4
02:08:46.410 --> 02:08:49.400 
奠边府是个错误  一个军事错误
Dien Bien Phu was an error.A military mistake.

5
02:08:49.610 --> 02:08:51.880 
错误?  是个故意的错误!
A mistake? A voluntary mistake!

6
02:08:52.080 --> 02:08:53.780 
故意的!
Voluntary!

7
02:08:55.720 --> 02:08:57.980 
所有士兵都知道
All the soldiers knew.

8
02:08:58.220 --> 02:08:59.920 
我们知道自己会死
We knew we would be dead.

9
02:08:59.920 --> 02:09:01.620 
那些将军和上校以为
The generals and the colonels believe it's impossible for the Viets...

10
02:09:01.760 --> 02:09:05.520 
越南人不可能运大炮上山
to get the cannon up there in the mountains.

11
02:09:05.730 --> 02:09:07.160 
但他们办到了
But they do.

12
02:09:07.430 --> 02:09:10.860 
然后等着下雨
Then they wait for the rain to come.

